headline: America’s F-35 is stealthy in combat but lights up the radar in Trump’s trade war
summary: The latest blowback came after Trump’s 39% tariff on Switzerland went into effect, prompting lawmakers there to demand the government scrap its F-35 order.

headline: Spacecraft-Maker Firefly Shoots for the Moon in Nasdaq Debut
